        [
          "Sell your Services. You're a great fighter, an excellent protector, and a good asset to any side that will have you, and you know it. You've even got information on their rival Sect, having worked with it as \"Expendable Pander Fodder\" But you also know that You're not the one holding the cards here. So you're willing to make Deals."
        ],
        [
          "Keep your Secret. You've got valuable information on Who made you and how, and what they're likely to be doing, but the price of that is INSANELY high, considering you'd have to divulge how you learned it."
        ],
        [
          "Stay Ahead of your old masters and keep your freedom. Better Final Death than recapture."
